/blockquote><br />\n如果係一個普通人係香港除非出賣自己勞力（但要考慮自己老左仲做唔做得黎），如果唔係既話，學歷的確重要<br />\n<br />\n如果你係一個有才既人（係mark zuckerberg同bill gates個d才華），無學歷都可以有出路<br />\n<br />\n巴打要慎重考慮退學依件事，不如試下專心讀下先啦，停一停part time（定係你係返緊長工，讀hd part time？）"},{"pid":"fb248f34d65aef1262bee80fddf4459a1855e006","tid":466461,"uid":4824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇下你讀d咩</blockquote><br />\n暫時讀梗IT方面 <br />\n但好多人都覺得我唔岩尼一科</blockquote><br />\nIt咩科？"},{"pid":"454e7a325767bb783fc1c921fe847bf5e8f58e21","tid":466461,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:02:56.000Z","msg":"點解唔做<del>保險狗</del>財務策劃師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7131b49f43aed1aaf6ce985070b69f78d20bae2","tid":466461,"uid":37648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"同問。。想疊埋心水考消防入境海關算<br />\n一邊做電工學徒一邊考"},{"pid":"217b8a2fb1adb3bed24f3ff2558e86a527974d5b","tid":466461,"uid":129506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"中學出黎直接入政府<br />\n<br />\n揾2雞幾又穩定，都唔差啊<br />\n<br />\n但揾唔到大錢咁解"},{"pid":"bd2215be6a9126b3a3433e71a6cfed72c6b49dd3","tid":466461,"uid":49853,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"唔讀書的確死路一條<br />\n但偏偏唔係個個都係讀書料"},{"pid":"85283fa30c32ce56b14b75cff03837e922d0bcee","tid":466461,"uid":83016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"如果你夢想係做會計師 咁唔讀書真係冇出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你冇夢想 咁唔讀又有乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0421a3cb1defaa2e5419e9c8c545757988528b","tid":466461,"uid":126681,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:15:34.000Z","msg":"要學識錢搵錢"},{"pid":"aff81d6ba94241d32fc0c9cb019588a965207237","tid":466461,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:17:57.000Z","msg":"唔讀而因爲無讀有好出路嘅眞係唔多。有啲嘢嘅分別只係有同無，大個仔要識諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745f778c3161525fce0bcd5631ef3b273ae14acb","tid":466461,"uid":133988,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:21:27.000Z","msg":"你係連登問 你會唔會係錯地方問?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登個個都話唔好讀死書 學位無用咖啦啲人<br />\n但係有幾多個知道現實情況?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多職位 就係睇你張沙紙 <br />\n唔理你HEA讀番黎又好 努力讀番黎又好<br />\n你夠資格 你既人工就有得上升<br />\n除非你甘心停留係低位 人工去到上限就停囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇你點睇<br />\n再者 學歷唔高 但搵到大錢 又有幾多個?"},{"pid":"01c9de8ff25cc35c4d4d698dbab6757d5607e7f1","tid":466461,"uid":58316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:37:50.000Z","msg":"讀商科<br />\n受夠私人市場<br />\n始終都係aim政府工<br />\n做緊n仔儲經驗（利申ff）<br />\n老土講學歷=入場券<br />\n今時今日做得入境海關aco都預你大學生"},{"pid":"21444f9e966736fa1a7b3ea90cedb2e6d3108b75","tid":466461,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇下你讀d咩</blockquote><br />\n暫時讀梗IT方面 <br />\n但好多人都覺得我唔岩尼一科</blockquote><br />\n就算Google Facebook都有engineer冇degree，不過佢地從工作經驗學習同埋自學，佢地嘅知識已經多過一個degree畢業<br />\n<br />\n所以唔返學係Okay嘅，不過自學要勁囉"},{"pid":"078eab5042d760796f06787887d1a75c229ca7f1","tid":466461,"uid":119695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:50:37.000Z","msg":"要睇你有冇父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a108f6f3733cd2454f320ee112dc2b520deb84f","tid":466461,"uid":105552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:52:36.000Z","msg":"講真 讀IVE 除非你本身爭少少上到大學個D<br />\n或者突然之間性情大變 好努力咁讀書<br />\n或者有某種原因驅使你<br />\n如果唔係不如早D出黎做野..."}]}